'''Trang Robotics''' was a family-owned corporation that had a long and respected history. Based on the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] [[Drewwa]] in the [[Almanian system]], the company's headquarters were lavish and featured workshops staffed by master-craftsmen. They manufactured the [[Duelist Elite/Legends|Duelist Elite]] [[fencing]] [[Training droid/Legends|training droid]].<ref name="EGTD" />

The success of the Duelist Elite led to the creation of the formidable [[GX1-series battle droid]]. During the [[Second Galactic Civil War]], they constructed tiny acrobat droids.

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Author [[Daniel Wallace]] named this company after his son, Grant.<ref name="Dan">{{Blog|danwallace|72|Forgotten Easter Eggs}}</ref>

